    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lycans Returns </strong>es el primer juego del Universo de <strong>Gallery of Shadows</strong> un Universo de <strong>Fantasía Oscura</strong> basado en monstruos clásicos y otros seres fantásticos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/805d13d1e451313a218360eb2a878e97.avif?t=1768321808\" width=540 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/fc1dd1e26c4fc0647f75058f1a56c8ea.avif?t=1768321808\" width=327 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >En el juego tomas el papel de un &quot;<strong>Lycan</strong>&quot; un Hombre Lobo el cual viene de la <strong>Isla Lycan</strong> con la misión recuperar &quot;<strong>Las Tierras del Sur</strong>&quot; los cuales fueron territorios que su especie dominaba siglos atrás y que ahora está bajo el control de los humanos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f9bb74810ea1d7815bfe13f2e093bcf0.avif?t=1768321808\" width=327 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tu misión es recuperar las 4 zonas invadidas por los humanos &quot;<strong>La Granja</strong>,  <strong>Altonian</strong>, <strong>Fortoria</strong> y <strong>Poman</strong>&quot;  cazando humanos durante la noche y subiendo la barra de miedo de cada zona para conquistarlas y así lograr que los <strong>Lycans</strong> vuelvan a dominar <strong>Las Tierras del Sur</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/aa11f8a3c04383f7059c8b80b221789f.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/aa11f8a3c04383f7059c8b80b221789f.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/aa11f8a3c04383f7059c8b80b221789f.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pero ten cuidado,  si un humano te ve no va a tardar en alertarse y correr y si un <strong>Oficial</strong> te detecta este alertará a los demás y tocará la campana para llamar a un <strong>Cazador</strong> que te llevará a sus mazmorras si es que te logra capturar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/452ed8e4b9096b35bbd6b6e688ecd090.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/452ed8e4b9096b35bbd6b6e688ecd090.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/452ed8e4b9096b35bbd6b6e688ecd090.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>CAMINA ENTRE LOS HUMANOS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >De día puedes usar tu forma humana para interactuar con los humanos y conocer la historia alrededor de la <strong>Purga Lycan</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/a73d9d40b7e77fd5a6b4c0a6daa73ffd.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/a73d9d40b7e77fd5a6b4c0a6daa73ffd.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/a73d9d40b7e77fd5a6b4c0a6daa73ffd.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>CONOCE OTRAS CRIATURAS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El Universo de <strong>Gallery of Shadows</strong> está lleno de <strong>Criaturas y Monstruos</strong> y en<strong> Lycans Returns</strong> conocerás a algunas de ellas que pueden ayudarte en tu misión de recuperar &quot;<strong>Las Tierras del Sur</strong>&quot;<strong> </strong>habla con ellas y descubre sus historias.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f7b81500524d07ba3cf28eda7498c522.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f7b81500524d07ba3cf28eda7498c522.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f7b81500524d07ba3cf28eda7498c522.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PERSONALIZA A TU GUSTO</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A parte de tu misión principal también tendrás a tu disposición un territorio el cual puedes mejorar partiendo de un <strong>Campamento</strong> a una <strong>Mansión</strong> además de poder vestirte con cierta cantidad de trajes que podrás conseguir a lo largo del juego.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/b5cad709f776c7a5f63cff94a282fbb5.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/b5cad709f776c7a5f63cff94a282fbb5.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/b5cad709f776c7a5f63cff94a282fbb5.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f15a3f56bd9b72a49baf9783a3d7c342.poster.avif?t=1768321808\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f15a3f56bd9b72a49baf9783a3d7c342.webm?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895640/extras/f15a3f56bd9b72a49baf9783a3d7c342.mp4?t=1768321808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
